snippet.title: Thats My Family - Family Fun Night SWITCH Trailer
snippet.description:
Family Fun Night is the first game from That's My Family to offer both original board games and classic games that were part of your childhood! Play 14 different games, from Snakes and Ladders to Parcheesi, Chess and 4 in a Row, and many more!

It's time for Family Fun Night! Relive family nights from different eras and environments!

Find more information about the game on our website:
https://www.justforgames.com/family-fun-night/
 
That's My Family - Family Fun Night will be available exclusively on Nintendo Switch on Spring 2023. A retail edition will be available in Europe on the same day.
